====Stealth Democracy:====

What is the RPA really about?
The International Party of Ricksism is about the movement towards world domination. We will take over governments using a unique term called, Stealth Democracy.

Short Term Goal: 
Gain members into the lower and upper party.

Long Term Goal: 
RPA dominence of American politics and government.
World Domination under our government.

World Domination, How?
Gain a two thirds majority in the House of Representitives (290) and Senate (67)
And 1 President into the Executive Branch.

We do this threw a process called stealth democracy. Basically we have our members act like normal democrats and republicans (concealing their true agenda and identity as the RPA). We sit and get them elected until we have the nessesary numbers in government.

Once we have the numbers we use congress to impeach all the surpreme court judges. Then we use the president to select RPA approved members and have them confirmed by the majority RPA Congress. Once the judges have been placed we are legally free to change the government anyway we want.

Initiate RPA reforms to monopolize our control of the [[government]] and begin our new foreign policy programs.


